---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="St. Patrick's Day — Unmasking the Holidays — Nazaryah" description="St. Patrick merged Celtic paganism with Catholic Christianity — placing the sun on the cross, using the pagan triskele, absorbing pagan sacred sites.">
  <div class="hol-wrap">
    <section class="hol-hero">
      <p class="hol-series">&#8213; Unmasking the Holidays · March &#8213;</p>
      <h1 class="hol-title">St. Patrick's Day</h1>
      <p class="hol-sub">15 Traditions. The sun on the cross. The syncretism Deuteronomy 12 forbids.</p>
    </section>
    <section class="hol-section">
      <div class="hol-prose">
        <p>St. Patrick's Day (March 17th) celebrates the man who merged Celtic paganism with Catholic Christianity. Patrick placed the sun on the cross to create the Celtic cross — not as decoration, but as deliberate syncretism, superimposing the solar symbol onto the symbol of the Messiah to make the new faith accessible to sun worshippers.</p>
        <p>He used the shamrock — connected to the pagan triskele, a triple spiral representing the three-stage cycle of life, death, and rebirth in Celtic sun religion — to teach the unbiblical doctrine of the Trinity. He absorbed pagan sacred sites, sacred fires (Beltane), and sacred dates into the Catholic system. He is celebrated for doing exactly what Deuteronomy 12 forbids: worshipping Yahuah using the methods of the pagans.</p>
        <p>This study examines 15 St. Patrick's Day traditions and exposes the syncretism at the heart of how Ireland was "converted."</p>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="hol-coming">
      <div class="hol-coming-inner">
        <div class="hol-coming-icon">&#9685;</div>
        <h2 class="hol-coming-title">Full Study Coming</h2>
        <p>This study is being assembled. Return to the <a href="/holidays" class="hol-link">Holidays hub</a> or explore <a href="/sun-worship/sacred-act" class="hol-link">The Sacred Act</a> while this page is built.</p>
      </div>
    </section>
    <div class="hol-nav">
      <a href="/holidays/valentines-day" class="hol-nav-link">&#8592; Valentine's Day</a>
      <a href="/holidays/easter" class="hol-nav-link">Easter &#8594;</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
<style>
  .hol-wrap { background:linear-gradient(180deg,#0e0904 0%,#1a1208 20%,#160f07 100%); color:#f0e0bf; font-family:'Crimson Pro','Crimson Text',Georgia,serif; min-height:80vh; }
  .hol-hero { text-align:center; padding:5rem 1.5rem 3.5rem; border-bottom:1px solid #4a3218; background:radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 0%,rgba(26,74,26,0.25),transparent 70%),linear-gradient(180deg,#0a0602 0%,#1a1208 100%); }
  .hol-series { font-family:'Cinzel',serif; font-size:10px; letter-spacing:4px; color:#8a6028; text-transform:uppercase; margin-bottom:.75rem; }
  .hol-title { font-family:'Cinzel',serif; font-size:clamp(2rem,6vw,3.5rem); font-weight:700; color:#f0e0bf; margin:0 0 .75rem; border-bottom:3px solid #1a4a1a; display:inline-block; padding-bottom:.5rem; }
  .hol-sub { font-size:1.1rem; color:#c4a46b; font-style:italic; max-width:520px; margin:1rem auto 0; line-height:1.6; }
  .hol-section { padding:3.5rem 1.5rem; border-bottom:1px solid #2e1f0d; max-width:720px; margin:0 auto; }
  .hol-prose { font-size:1.1rem; line-height:1.85; color:#d9c9a8; }
  .hol-prose p { margin-bottom:1.4rem; }
  .hol-coming { padding:3.5rem 1.5rem; text-align:center; background:rgba(10,6,2,.3); border-bottom:1px solid #2e1f0d; }
  .hol-coming-inner { max-width:560px; margin:0 auto; }
  .hol-coming-icon { font-size:2rem; color:#5a3a10; margin-bottom:1rem; }
  .hol-coming-title { font-family:'Cinzel',serif; font-size:1.3rem; font-weight:600; color:#c4a46b; margin:0 0 1rem; }
  .hol-coming p { font-size:1rem; color:#a89060; line-height:1.75; }
  .hol-link { color:#BA7517; text-decoration:underline; text-underline-offset:3px; }
  .hol-link:hover { color:#d4930f; }
  .hol-nav { display:flex; justify-content:space-between; padding:1.75rem 2rem; max-width:720px; margin:0 auto; }
  .hol-nav-link { font-family:'Cinzel',serif; font-size:10px; letter-spacing:1.5px; text-transform:uppercase; color:#6a4820; text-decoration:none; }
  .hol-nav-link:hover { color:#BA7517; }
</style>
